-- Huawei Technologies to Invest $2 Billion in India, People's Daily Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-14T08:09:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-14/huawei-technologies-to-invest-2-billion-in-india-people-s-daily-reports.html
China’s Huawei Technologies Co. will
invest $2 billion in India in the next five years to expand
production and development efforts in the country, the People’s
Daily newspaper reported on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
